name: Space Farmer (Mikeeyy)
description:
This is an entry for the https://itch.io/jam/gamedevjs-2020 gamejam made in Godot in a little under 2 weeks. Some of the development was streamed on my twitch https://www.twitch.tv/mikeyboonn come check it out!

Build your garden in space! Why? Just for the fun of it! Please leave your feedback in the comments, it would be much appreciated.

If you don't want to unlock everything by playing you can do it in the menu at the top left.

Safari users may have problems. If the game doesn't load please try another browser.

All programming and visual art by me. 

Thanks to The_Coding_Geek, FJTilter, tehsquidge and Ryuno-Ki on Discord for playtesting!

Music from :

https://opengameart.org/content/space-orchestral
